# Mad Libs Generator

## Repository
https://github.com/MichelleC06/MAD-LIBS-GENERATOR

## Description
The mad libs generator will create a list to store all inputs in order to put each of them into their designated section in the mad lib. There will be 2 Mad Lib options to pick from
alongside the adjectives, nouns, and verbs that will be put into them. The goal is to create a fun experience that uses a list effectively without error. 

## Features
- Input Noun, Verb, or Adjective
	- allows the user to pick the word they want inserted in the story. 
- Pick a Mad Lib
	- allows the user to pick the story based on the titles given to them to mad lib. 
- Play again
	-allows the user to play again and start from the top of the program after finishing the Mad Lib. 

## Challenges,
- making sure the lists are integrated properly.
- figuring out how to incorporate multiple mad lib options, on top of different inserts for each story.
- Making sure the VES code can run properly due to prior issues with the program. 

